title: GetDevObjPropReferenceFromContents (Function)
text:
FUNCTION GetDevObjPropReferenceFromContents :
BACnetDevObjPropReference
Tries to evaluate property contents as BACnetDevObjPropReference data type. If the contents are not of type BACnetDevObjPropReference
0 is returned.

rows.Name: conts
rows.Comment: The contents to be evaluated asBACnetDevObjPropReference.
